import math
n = int(input())
for i in range(1, n + 1):
    (a, b) = map(int, input().split())
    c = math.pow(a, 2)
    d = math.pow(b, 2)
    q = c + d
    w = abs(c - d)
    x = math.sqrt(q)
    y = math.sqrt(w)
    print(round(y, 4), round(x, 4))
